it drives the host insane.

988
01:17:47,328 --> 01:17:49,997
It's like it feeds off
all the bad shit in their head,

989
01:17:50,081 --> 01:17:52,333
and then once it's done feeding,

990
01:17:52,417 --> 01:17:55,253
it forces the host to kill
themself in front of a witness.

991
01:17:55,336 --> 01:17:57,755
And then that witness
becomes the new host.

992
01:17:57,839 --> 01:17:59,423
That's how you got it from Lewis.

993
01:17:59,507 --> 01:18:01,675
It was passed to Lewis by a cop in Jersey.

994
01:18:01,759 --> 01:18:03,844
That cop was the first one
I tried to contact,

995
01:18:03,928 --> 01:18:05,262
but I guess he went off the grid.

996
01:18:05,346 --> 01:18:07,700
